Change 'your JIRA administrator' to 'a user with Administer Projects permission'.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *JIRA Software Cloud*. Using *JIRA Software Server*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSWSERVER-14641].
  {panel}

When the "Greenhopper Project Progress" gadget is on the system dashboard, it is displayed on the login page for not logged in users.
It displays an error message "The project no longer exists." since there is no access for anonymous users.
Please see the attached screenshot.
